                    <body>
                              <pb n="1"/>
                              <p rend="align(right)">
                                        <placeName>St Louis</placeName>
                                        <del>March</del>
                                        <date>Aprl 4/53</date>
                              </p>
                              <p>
                                        <addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(2)">Dear Sir</p>
                              <p rend="indent(3)">having five dollars<lb/> to spare I thought it
                                        could not<lb/> be put to a better use than the<lb/> one to
                                        which it is applied to</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">you will please place it<lb/> to my a/c. I wish
                                        you to put<lb/> down my name for <persName>Dias</persName>
                                        letters<lb/> I do not know <sic>wether</sic> the Bible<lb/>
                                        I have subscribed for will be bound<lb/> as I have no
                                        recollection however<lb/> if it should happen that the
                                        six<lb/> dollars only pays for it in a paper<lb/> cover you
                                        will please have it<lb/> Bound in plain Leather as<lb/> I
                                        expect it can be done better &amp;<lb/> cheaper in your city
                                        than here<lb/> you would also oblige me<lb/> if you can find
                                        time to send<lb/> me my a/c by so doing you<lb/> will oblige
                                        yours very</p>
                              <p rend="indent(11)">
                                        <sic>Respectfuly</sic>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(12)">
                                        <persName role="author">H Myers</persName>
                              </p>
                              <p>
                                        <hi rend="underline">Box 15 15</hi>
                              </p>
                              <pb n="2"/>
                              <p>
                                        <addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee>
                              </p>
